        <updateDate>2021-04-19T19:34:06Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Monarch and Pollinator Highway Act of 2021 or the</b> <b>MPH Act of 20</b><strong>21</strong><strong></strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Transportation to provide grants to states, Indian tribes, and federal land management agencies to carry out pollinator-friendly practices on roadsides and highway rights-of-way, including the planting and seeding of native, locally-appropriate grasses, wildflowers, and milkweed.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
